## Block 22 — Frontend: [main.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/main.js) & [router/index.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/router/index.js)

**Files:** [frontend/src/main.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/main.js), [frontend/src/router/index.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/router/index.js)

**[main.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/main.js)** — standard Vue 3 entry point: creates the app, attaches the router, mounts to `#app`.

**Router** defines six page routes:

```
/                            → Home.vue           (upload files, start project)
/process/:projectId          → MainView.vue        (build graph, configure)
/simulation/:simulationId    → SimulationView.vue  (prepare agents, view config)
/simulation/:simulationId/start → SimulationRunView.vue (run + live feed)
/report/:reportId            → ReportView.vue      (read generated report)
/interaction/:reportId       → InteractionView.vue (chat with agents / Report Agent)
```

All IDs are passed as route props directly to the component — no extra Vuex/Pinia lookup needed.

---

## Block 23 — Frontend: [api/index.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/api/index.js) (HTTP Client)

**File:** [frontend/src/api/index.js](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/api/index.js)

Creates an **Axios** instance:
- `baseURL` from `VITE_API_BASE_URL` (defaults to `http://localhost:5001`).
- 5-minute timeout — some LLM operations are slow.
- **Response interceptor** — if the response has `success: false`, it converts the payload into a rejected `Promise`, so every API call can use `.catch()` uniformly.
- **[requestWithRetry(fn, maxRetries=3)](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/api/index.js#53-66)** — exported utility that wraps any API function with exponential back-off retries (doubles the delay on each retry).

