## Block 24 — Frontend: Views (Page Components)

| File | Role |
|---|---|
| [Home.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/Home.vue) | Landing page. File drag-and-drop, project name, simulation goal textarea. Calls `POST /api/graph/ontology/generate`. On success, navigates to `/process/:projectId`. |
| [MainView.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/MainView.vue) | Shows the generated ontology (entity types, relation types, a summary). Lets the user trigger graph build (`POST /api/graph/build`). Polls the task status until graph is complete, then navigates to simulation. |
| [SimulationView.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/SimulationView.vue) | Shows simulation metadata (entity count, entity types, profiles). Triggers `POST /api/simulation/prepare` and polls progress via animated stage steps. |
| [SimulationRunView.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/SimulationRunView.vue) | Runs the simulation (`POST /api/simulation/start`). Shows live post feed and round counter with animated Twitter/Reddit counters. Provides a Stop button. |
| [ReportView.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/ReportView.vue) | Polls for completed report sections incrementally. Renders Markdown with a library. Shows agent-log panel in real time. |
| [InteractionView.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/InteractionView.vue) | Chat interface. Lets the user choose "Chat with Report Agent" or "Interview Agent <name>". Maintains a conversation history array passed with every message. |
| [Process.vue](file:///f:/Courses/AIExperiments/MiroFish/frontend/src/views/Process.vue) | (Appears to be a combined super-view for the whole process pipeline, possibly used for different layout contexts.) |

